About Me

My 'passion' to explore new stuff. Maybe it is not just with me, all humans have curiosity. Be happy, make others happy. I have a lots of pieces of wisdom to share but if I continue, you will call me a hypocrite. I am an undergradute at IIT Bombay pursuing my major in Aerospace Engineering.
